updateWithJS cannot be used on tables that contain geometry columns.

```
import { SimpleDB } from '@nshiab/simple-data-analysis';
const sdb = new SimpleDB();
const table = sdb.newTable();
// Attempting to use updateWithJS on a table with geometries will throw an error
try {
  await table.updateWithJS((rows) => rows);
} catch (e) {
  console.error('Error:', e.message);
}
await sdb.done();
```

